{
  "stem": "747.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we just-- we were very subdued, where we-- we closed-- I remembered with Passover, we had the double windows in the living room--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in '39, '40, '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father put pillows between the windows-- the double windows-- that the sound shouldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the-- the house was close to the road-- I mean to the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But still we were home-- still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then my father was called into the labor force in '41.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was, at that time-- '41, he was in his early 50s.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they kept him for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was demolishing some old buildings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was not much to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they sent him home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was too old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the young ones, they called in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And little by little, hardly any men left in our town-- Jewish men.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were all sent out to the front and picking mines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just-- it was-- they had the registration in the city hall, and they knew of-- of everyone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It came in a telegram.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Telegram that he called into a certain unit, has to be in a certain time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A certain unit of labor-- battalion, they called it, in different cities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, they made it into units.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they sent them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My husband was working on the-- by the-- by the border-- Polish-Hungarian border, up in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- no, they were the leaders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They became the captains and the lieutenants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some were decent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of the them were not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of the sudden, it got into their head that they became somebodys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to-- to ruin-- to hurt the Jew-- it was-- it was an inhuman treatment in many of these battalions.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
